Edge Performance Bids for TV Production Firm Coolabi, Times Says

-- B y   G r a n t   S m i t h
-- 
2011-08-14T12:35:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-14/edge-performance-bids-for-tv-production-firm-coolabi-times-says.html
Edge Performance VCT Plc, a media
investment fund set up by Harvey Goldsmith and Pete Tong, has
made a bid for film and television production company  Coolabi
Plc (COO) , the  Sunday Times reported , without saying where it got the
information.  Coolabi, which has a market value of 4.9 million pounds ($8
million), said last week it had been approached by a bidder it
did not identify.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Grant Smith in London at 
